  "summary": {
    "as": "Reported to House",
    "asOf": "2022-02-18",
    "date": "2022-02-23T20:45:07Z",
    "text": "National Science and Technology Strategy Act of 2021\n\nThis bill requires the Office of Science and Technology Policy (OSTP) to develop a national science and technology strategy and publish a science and technology review.\n\nThe bill revises OSTP reporting requirements to direct the OSTP to submit to Congress a comprehensive national science and technology strategy of the United States to meet national research and development objectives for the following four-year period.\n\nNo later than December 31, 2022, and every four years afterwards, the OSTP shall complete a review of the science and technology enterprise of the United States."
  },
